response.overview: On November 20, 2017, Tokorozawa Citizen Gymnasium Main Arena in Tokorozawa hosted Day 3 of NJPW World Tag League 2017.  The main event featured CHAOS (Hirooki Goto, Tomohiro Ishii, Toru Yano & YOSHI-HASHI) vs Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL, SANADA, Tetsuya Naito & Hiromu Takahashi).  The card also featured BULLET CLUB (Bad Luck Fale & Chase Owens) vs TenKoji (Hiroyoshi Tenzan & Satoshi Kojima).  Other wrestlers on the show include Jeff Cobb, Michael Elgin, and Davey Boy Smith Jr., and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 3
